name: OMG!! They killed Kenny
description:
South Park Boys: Limited edition

Kenny has died 126 times in the South Park franchise. Kenny is the new lucky charm! For someone who has been beaten, shot, crushed, sundried, and more...he is still alive! This boy right here will bring you luck where ever you take him! Like, bruh!! Kenny is an unsung hero and always cares for his sister and his friends. Nobody understands what he is saying but his Bro got his back because that is what Broships is all about!!!
